{"tid":1584490,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"祖記fans不滿迪列特表現  網上諷刺「荷蘭菲爾鍾斯！」","createTime":"2019-09-21T06:47:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T05:26:30.000Z","uid":14075,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"efc8dfa0e6587e42e3bdfee9de8e627f1f872af8","tid":1584490,"uid":14075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T06:47:18.000Z","msg":"根據英國《每日郵報》報道，祖雲達斯球迷對6780萬鎊加盟的荷蘭中堅迪列特在歐聯對陣馬德里體育會的表現並不滿意，並稱這名20歲小將為「荷蘭版菲爾鍾斯」，以表示對他的不滿。<br />\n數場比賽中，迪列特的表現都遜於預期，攻強守弱的特點表露無遺。在歐聯首輪分組賽的兩球失球，都是頭球的失誤，令不少球迷都怪責任職中堅的迪列特。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2019/09/19/14/18673118-7482079-image-a-152_1568899664065.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2019%2F09%2F19%2F14%2F18673118-7482079-image-a-152_1568899664065.jpg&h=3ffcb324&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2019/09/19/15/18673122-7482079-image-a-8_1568904493390.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2019%2F09%2F19%2F15%2F18673122-7482079-image-a-8_1568904493390.jpg&h=451c8d30&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cc33b0900de7d3e7308bba5f7bc859cfdc0643a9","tid":1584490,"uid":60695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T06:48:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efc7d399ee0c7b46e62d498e00f37e0799642d76","tid":1584490,"uid":67225,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T06:57:44.000Z","msg":"鍾斯係攻守都弱<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d636b2bc43f760d32fed8214c21e60399df9cab","tid":1584490,"uid":73550,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T07:01:43.000Z","msg":"同我地鍾斯比is侮辱。。"},{"pid":"0fdd0ce939f3d264c51880ca0f18b09b778c584b","tid":1584490,"uid":50535,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T07:03:11.0